  "release_notes": "Fixes Microsoft Store purchase still hanging in v1.0.26. The same-process WinForms anchor window was created Minimized, which prevented the Store SDK from validating it as a usable overlay anchor. v1.0.27 removes the Minimized state and instead positions the 1x1 Opacity=0 form off-screen at (-32000, -32000) — invisible to the user but a real WS_VISIBLE window from the SDK's perspective. No other changes vs. v1.0.26.",
